gomodel:SYNGO_4709  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: STORM super-resolution imaging localized FUS to presynapses in cultured hippocampi (Figure 4), where it localizes closely to synaptic vescicles (Figure 5) and proximal to bassoon (Figure 6).. Experimental description: M&M: \"Immunolabeling of Rat Hippocampal Neurons for SMLM and Conventional Fluorescence Imaging\"\n\nantibody used for STORM:\nFUS, Sigma-Aldrich Cat# HPA008784 RRID:AB_1849181, 1:2000/1:500 (WB on NIH lysate/FI & STORM)" ;
